<h3 id="dominic-rizzo"><strong>Dominic Rizzo</strong></h3>
<p><strong>zeroRISC Inc.</strong></p>

<p><img src="../images/dominic-rizzo.png" alt="" style="width: 300px; float: left;
margin: 5px" /> <strong>Bio:</strong> Dominic Rizzo is co-founder and CEO of zeroRISC Inc., a RISC-V start-up focused on creating trust through transparency via the OpenTitan secure silicon ecosystem. He also founded OpenTitan, the first open source silicon root of trust project, which recently brought a chip to commercial fruition. He previously developed the first FIPS-certified U2F Security Key, and has research interests in secure silicon hardening, trustworthy authenticators, and formal methods for proof of implementation correctness.</p>

