<h3 id="silviu-chiricescu"><strong>Silviu Chiricescu</strong></h3>
<p><strong>DRAPER</strong></p>

<p><img src="../images/silviu-chiricescu.png" alt="" style="width: 300px; float: left;
margin: 5px" /> <strong>Bio:</strong> Silviu Chiricescu is a DMTS at Draper Laboratory where he is leading research into system-level security addressing issues at all the layers of the compute stack – from low-level hardware to the application. Prior to Draper, Chiricescu was with BAE Systems where he had led, in multiple capacities,  CRAD in the fields of cybersecurity, architecture, and networking.</p>
